{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_11_01",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の打ち合わせにて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.6000000318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……もし恋の新作？　第四弾？\nうちがそのヒロインに……抜擢！？",
      "startTime": 7.1333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。シリーズが好調で、新作の打診があったんだ\n優も以前から出たいって言ってたし、良かったら――",
      "startTime": 15.8333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "やった～！　めっちゃ嬉しい！\nもちろん引き受けます、ヒロイン役！",
      "startTime": 22.8666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、やっぱやりたいことは\n常日頃から口に出しとくもんやな～",
      "startTime": 29.2333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "運命の気まぐれか、はたまたうちのポテンシャルの\n賜物か……決まる時はこうして決まるんやな！",
      "startTime": 36.4333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.0666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "優はもし恋がリリースされた当初から\nずっと自分も出たいって言ってたしな",
      "startTime": 43.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　だってめっちゃ面白いやん、もし恋！\nうち、こういうノベルゲー大好きやからな",
      "startTime": 50.9333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、渚ちゃん、芽衣ちゃんの過去三作も\nしっかりやり込んで全エンド回収済みやし……",
      "startTime": 59.0333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.0000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちにもヒロイン役の話こんかな、出たいな～\nってめっっっちゃ期待してたんよ！",
      "startTime": 66.699961366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\nうちにもし恋の話、持ってきてくれて",
      "startTime": 73.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どういたしまして。先方には快諾だって伝えて\nおくよ。それで、出演するにあたってなんだけど……",
      "startTime": 80.3666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "分かってます。アンケートやろ？\n自分の理想の恋愛模様について書くってやつ",
      "startTime": 88.2666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.1333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "その辺の段取りは、怜ちゃん達から聞いてます\nうちの理想の恋愛観をベースにストーリー作るんやろ？",
      "startTime": 96.6666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その通りだ。話が早くて助かるよ\n期日は一週間後だと助かるんだが……",
      "startTime": 105.3333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.3333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。まぁ、明日でもうちは平気やけど\nきっとすぐアンケート用紙真っ黒になるからな",
      "startTime": 113.8000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "この世のありとあらゆる物語を読み込んできた\nうちにかかれば、全人類キュン死間違いなしや！",
      "startTime": 120.4000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.8000000001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（うーん……やる気があるのはいいんだが……）\n（前の三人は空回って苦戦したからな……はてさて）",
      "startTime": 129.2178400041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 135.3333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 136.2333333652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まさか本当に翌日に出してくれるとは……\nでも、ありがとう。アンケート確認したよ",
      "startTime": 141.2000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、当然やんか。鈴村優に二言はありません\nそれで、どうでした？",
      "startTime": 150.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "良かったよ。シチュエーションも展開も凄く\nキュンとするし、ゲームとしても面白そうだ",
      "startTime": 156.3000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "せやろせやろ？　いや～、アカシックレコード並の\nうちのオタクデータベースが火ぃ吹いてもうたわ……",
      "startTime": 164.6333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "ファンタジー、お仕事系、アイドルとの秘密の恋愛……\nアイデアが溢れて止まらんから困ったわ",
      "startTime": 173.8333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "優は同人誌活動もしてるから、アイデアを出したり\nストーリーをまとめたりはお手の物だな。ただ……",
      "startTime": 180.9827858228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、分かる。さすがにやりたいことが多過ぎな\n気はしてます。ゲーム一本に収まらんね、これは……",
      "startTime": 190.0000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、パート2とかエピソード0とか外伝とか\nビギニングとか、一杯作るんはどうやろ？",
      "startTime": 199.5000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら、勝手にゲームの仕様を変えない\nシリーズ化は言うほど簡単じゃないんだ",
      "startTime": 207.0333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "そないなこと分かってます\nけど……どれもうちがやりたいことなんよ",
      "startTime": 212.8000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんこれは、優がいいアイデアを沢山出して\nくれたからこその悩みだ。いいことではある",
      "startTime": 220.2181075823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "でも提出する前にもう少し方向性は絞った方がいい\n優が本当にやりたいことはどれか、良く考えてみてくれ",
      "startTime": 229.4000000318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "そうは言うてもなぁ……うちが一番やりたいこと……\nう～ん……",
      "startTime": 240.2333333652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 243.0666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 244.1666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 244.1666666985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（あの後、優は自分なりにストーリー案を絞り）\n（ゲーム会社との打ち合わせに臨んだのだが……）",
      "startTime": 249.2666666985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 252.866659546
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
